<note n="0423002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0423002">鍱＝葉【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0423003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0423003">起＝於【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0424001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0424001">為＝真【明】</note>
<note n="0424002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0424002">無聞＝無間【宮】</note>
<note n="0424003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0424003">其＋（識）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0425001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0425001">諸＝識【宮】</note>
<note n="0425002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0425002">先＝光【聖】</note>
<note n="0425003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0425003">俗＋（故）【元】【明】【聖】</note>
<note n="0426001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426001">大炬＝火炬【宮】</note>
<note n="0426002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426002">筏＝栰【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0426003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426003">經＝逕【聖】</note>
<note n="0426004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426004">殖＝植【明】</note>
<note n="0426005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426005">作如＝即作【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0426006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426006">我今＝以我【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0426007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426007">頗梨＝玻瓈【明】下同</note>
<note n="0426008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426008">頗梨＝玻<g ref="#CB00742">󰋦</g>【宋】【元】【宮】下同，玻瓈【明】下同</note>
<note n="0426009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426009">眾＝烏【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
